Class AdminService

java.lang.Object
com.example.lab9.service.AdminService
@Service public class AdminService extends Object
Service class for managing Admin entities and related operations. Provides business logic for creating, retrieving, deleting admins, and managing associated entities like customers, employees, and orders.
